720153f-a.title: Manhattan: Greenwich Avenue - Christopher Street
720153f-a.text:
Greenwich Avenue, east side, north from Christopher Street to 30
Greenwich Avenue north of 10th Street, showing old Jefferson
Market and the old jail. Subway construction is going on under-
hneath Greenwich Avenue.
August 20, 1927.
L. Sperr.
